Underwater Cave

The underwater cave has a large opening filled with precious ores and rocks. Beautiful underwater plants grow along the cave's walls. Many paths lead deeper into the caves, but exploring them is dangerous.

Underwater Cave is a location that can be found in the Syrenthia region.

Keyword

The following keywords apply to this location.

Underwater

Faction

Underwater Cave is a member of the following factions:

Syrenthia

Activities

The following activities always available at this location.

Cave diving
Explore underwater cave
Mine tarsilium ore (Underwater)
Mine volcanic rock

Emergency Activity

These Emergency Activities are only visible if you are missing key items for traveling, and are there to prevent softlocks.

Emergency swim escape

Routes
